<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>FasaFas — Backend Developer Portal</title>
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#060e1a;--bg2:#0a1525;--bg3:#0f1e35;--card:#0c1828;
  --border:#172540;--accent:#2563eb;--accent2:#3b82f6;--accent3:#60a5fa;
  --green:#10b981;--amber:#f59e0b;--red:#ef4444;--purple:#8b5cf6;
  --teal:#14b8a6;--pink:#ec4899;--orange:#f97316;
  --text:#e2e8f0;--text2:#94a3b8;--text3:#475569;
  --font:'Segoe UI',system-ui,sans-serif;--mono:'Consolas','SF Mono',monospace;
  --sidebar:248px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html,body{height:100%;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--font);font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px;height:4px}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--border);border-radius:4px}

/* ════════ LOGIN ════════ */
#login-screen{
  position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:9999;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 50%,rgba(37,99,235,.14),transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 15%,rgba(16,185,129,.08),transparent 50%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 90%,rgba(139,92,246,.08),transparent 50%),
    var(--bg);
}
.login-box{
  width:100%;max-width:430px;
  background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:18px;
  padding:40px 36px;box-shadow:0 28px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.7);
}
.login-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:26px}
.login-logo-dot{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);animation:blink 1.4s infinite}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3}}
.login-logo-text{font-size:21px;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent2);letter-spacing:-.4px}
.login-logo-badge{
  margin-left:auto;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:6px;
  background:rgba(16,185,129,.12);border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.3);
  color:#6ee7b7;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase;
}
.login-title{font-size:22px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin-bottom:4px}
.login-sub{color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:26px;line-height:1.6}

.lf-group{margin-bottom:16px}
.lf-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:6px;display:block}
.lf-input{width:100%;padding:12px 14px;border-radius:9px;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text);font-family:var(--font);font-size:14px;outline:none;transition:border-color .15s,box-shadow .15s}
.lf-input:focus{border-color:var(--green);box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(16,185,129,.10)}
.lf-input::placeholder{color:var(--text3)}
.lf-pw-wrap{position:relative}
.lf-pw-wrap .lf-input{padding-right:44px}
.lf-eye{position:absolute;right:13px;top:50%;transform:translateY(-50%);background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text3);font-size:16px}
.lf-eye:hover{color:var(--text2)}

.login-error{background:rgba(239,68,68,.10);border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.25);border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:13px;color:#fca5a5;margin-bottom:14px;display:none;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.login-error.show{display:flex}

.login-btn{width:100%;padding:13px;border-radius:10px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#059669,#2563eb);color:#fff;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:all .2s;font-family:var(--font);margin-top:4px;letter-spacing:-.1px}
.login-btn:hover{opacity:.9;transform:translateY(-1px);box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(16,185,129,.25)}
.login-btn:disabled{opacity:.5;cursor:not-allowed;transform:none}

.creds-card{background:rgba(16,185,129,.06);border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.18);border-radius:10px;padding:14px 16px;margin-top:18px}
.creds-title{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:var(--green);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1px;margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.cred-row{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:6px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.1)}
.cred-row:last-child{border:none}
.cred-key{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px;min-width:80px}
.cred-val{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);flex:1;padding:0 8px}
.cred-use{background:none;border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.3);border-radius:5px;padding:2px 10px;font-size:10px;color:var(--green);cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--font);transition:all .15s}
.cred-use:hover{background:rgba(16,185,129,.12)}

.login-footer{margin-top:18px;text-align:center;font-size:11px;color:var(--text3)}
.login-footer a{color:var(--accent3);cursor:pointer}
.login-footer a:hover{text-decoration:underline}

/* ════════ APP LAYOUT ════════ */
#app-screen{display:none;height:100vh;overflow:hidden}
.app-layout{display:flex;height:100%}

/* Sidebar */
.sidebar{width:var(--sidebar);min-width:var(--sidebar);background:var(--bg2);border-right:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;flex-direction:column;overflow:hidden}
.sb-top{padding:16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0}
.sb-logo{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-size:16px;font-weight:900;color:var(--accent2);letter-spacing:-.3px}
.sb-logo-dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);animation:blink 1.4s infinite}
.sb-logo-tag{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;background:rgba(16,185,129,.12);color:#6ee7b7;border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.2);letter-spacing:.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.sb-user{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:12px 16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0}
.sb-av{width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:7px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#059669,#2563eb);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;flex-shrink:0}
.sb-uname{font-size:13px;font-weight:700}
.sb-urole{font-size:10px;color:var(--green);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}

.sb-nav{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:6px 0}
.sb-section{font-size:9px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:1.5px;color:var(--text3);padding:10px 16px 3px}
.sb-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:8px 16px;color:var(--text3);cursor:pointer;transition:all .15s;border-left:3px solid transparent;font-size:13px;font-weight:500}
.sb-item:hover{background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text2);border-left-color:var(--border)}
.sb-item.active{background:rgba(16,185,129,.08);color:var(--green);border-left-color:var(--green)}
.sb-icon{font-size:14px;width:18px;text-align:center;flex-shrink:0}
.sb-tag{margin-left:auto;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text3);font-size:9px;font-weight:700;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:4px}
.sb-tag.new{background:rgba(16,185,129,.12);border-color:rgba(16,185,129,.25);color:var(--green)}

.sb-bottom{padding:12px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0}
.logout-btn{width:100%;padding:8px;border-radius:7px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--text3);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--font);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:6px;transition:all .15s}
.logout-btn:hover{border-color:var(--red);color:#fca5a5;background:rgba(239,68,68,.07)}

/* Main */
.app-main{flex:1;overflow:hidden;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.topbar{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 28px;height:54px;background:var(--bg2);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);flex-shrink:0}
.topbar-title{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.tb-icon{font-size:17px}
.topbar-right{display:flex;gap:8px}
.tb-btn{padding:6px 13px;border-radius:7px;border:1px solid var(--border);background:transparent;color:var(--text2);font-size:12px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--font);transition:all .15s;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:5px}
.tb-btn:hover{background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text);border-color:var(--accent2)}

.content{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:28px 32px}
.panel{display:none}.panel.active{display:block}

/* ── Typography ── */
.ph1{font-size:20px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin-bottom:6px}
.ph2{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-.2px;margin:26px 0 12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.ph2:first-child{margin-top:0}
.ph2-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent2);flex-shrink:0}
.ph3{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;color:var(--accent3);margin:0 0 10px}
.pdesc{color:var(--text2);font-size:13px;margin-bottom:20px;line-height:1.7}

/* ── Grid ── */
.g2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px}
.g3{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:14px}
.g4{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:12px}
@media(max-width:900px){.g3{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}.g4{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr}}

/* ── Cards ── */
.card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:20px}
.stat-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:18px}
.stat-label{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.8px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:5px}
.stat-val{font-size:24px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.5px;margin-bottom:3px}
.stat-sub{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3)}

/* ── Feature list ── */
.fl{list-style:none}
.fl li{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:8px;padding:5px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(23,37,64,.7);font-size:12.5px;color:var(--text2)}
.fl li:last-child{border:none}
.fl li::before{content:'→';color:var(--green);font-size:11px;margin-top:2px;flex-shrink:0}

/* ── Code / endpoint ── */
.code-block{background:#050d18;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;padding:16px 18px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.9;overflow-x:auto;margin:10px 0;position:relative}
.code-copy{position:absolute;top:10px;right:10px;background:var(--bg3);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:5px;padding:3px 9px;font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);cursor:pointer;font-family:var(--font);transition:all .15s}
.code-copy:hover{border-color:var(--green);color:var(--green)}
.kw{color:#f472b6}.str{color:#6ee7b7}.com{color:#334d66}.fn{color:#60a5fa}.num{color:#fcd34d}.ty{color:#c4b5fd}.op{color:#94a3b8}

.ep{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;background:#050d18;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:7px;padding:9px 14px;margin:4px 0;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12.5px}
.meth{padding:2px 7px;border-radius:3px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0;letter-spacing:.3px}
.GET{background:rgba(16,185,129,.18);color:#6ee7b7}
.POST{background:rgba(37,99,235,.18);color:#93c5fd}
.PUT{background:rgba(245,158,11,.18);color:#fcd34d}
.DEL{background:rgba(239,68,68,.18);color:#fca5a5}
.WS{background:rgba(139,92,246,.18);color:#c4b5fd}
.ep-path{color:var(--text2);flex:1}
.ep-note{color:var(--text3);font-size:11px}

/* ── DB schema ── */
.schema{background:#050d18;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;overflow:hidden;margin:10px 0}
.schema-head{background:rgba(16,185,129,.07);padding:8px 14px;font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--green);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.schema-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:170px 140px 1fr;gap:8px;padding:6px 14px;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(23,37,64,.6);font-size:12px;font-family:var(--mono)}
.schema-row:last-child{border:none}
.sr-field{color:var(--text)}
.sr-field.pk{color:var(--amber)}
.sr-field.fk{color:var(--teal)}
.sr-type{color:var(--purple)}
.sr-note{color:var(--text3);font-size:11px}

/* ── Badge ── */
.badge{display:inline-flex;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:10px;font-weight:700}
.bg{background:rgba(16,185,129,.15);color:#6ee7b7;border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,.25)}
.ba{background:rgba(37,99,235,.15);color:#93c5fd;border:1px solid rgba(37,99,235,.25)}
.bp{background:rgba(139,92,246,.15);color:#c4b5fd;border:1px solid rgba(139,92,246,.25)}
.bam{background:rgba(245,158,11,.15);color:#fcd34d;border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.25)}
.br{background:rgba(239,68,68,.15);color:#fca5a5;border:1px solid rgba(239,68,68,.25)}
.bt{background:rgba(20,184,166,.15);color:#5eead4;border:1px solid rgba(20,184,166,.25)}

/* ── Service card ── */
.svc-card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:9px;padding:16px}
.svc-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:4px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.svc-desc{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:10px}
.svc-tags{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.svc-tag{font-size:10px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text3);border:1px solid var(--border)}

/* ── Infra card ── */
.infra-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:10px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(23,37,64,.6)}
.infra-item:last-child{border:none}
.infra-dot{width:8px;height:8px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:6px}
.infra-title{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:2px}
.infra-desc{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--text2)}

/* ── Toast ── */
.toast{position:fixed;bottom:24px;right:24px;z-index:9999;background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--green);border-radius:10px;padding:11px 18px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;color:var(--text);font-size:13px;font-weight:600;transform:translateY(80px);opacity:0;transition:all .3s;box-shadow:0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}
.toast.show{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="toast" id="toast"></div>

<!-- ════════════════════════════════
     LOGIN SCREEN
════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="login-screen">
  <div class="login-box">
    <div class="login-logo">
      <div class="login-logo-dot"></div>
      <div class="login-logo-text">FasaFas</div>
      <div class="login-logo-badge">⚙️ Dev Portal</div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="login-title">Backend Developer Access</h2>
    <p class="login-sub">Restricted to authorised engineers only. Enter your developer credentials to view the backend architecture, APIs, and database schema.</p>

    <div class="login-error" id="login-error">
      <span>⚠</span><span id="err-msg">Invalid credentials. Access denied.</span>
    </div>

    <div class="lf-group">
      <label class="lf-label">Developer Username</label>
      <input class="lf-input" id="l-user" type="text" placeholder="dev@fasafas.com" autocomplete="username"
        onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')document.getElementById('l-pass').focus()">
    </div>
    <div class="lf-group">
      <label class="lf-label">Password</label>
      <div class="lf-pw-wrap">
        <input class="lf-input" id="l-pass" type="password" placeholder="Developer password"
          onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter')doLogin()">
        <button class="lf-eye" onclick="togglePw()">👁</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <button class="login-btn" id="login-btn" onclick="doLogin()">Access Developer Portal →</button>

    <!-- Credentials hint -->
    <div class="creds-card">
      <div class="creds-title">🔑 Developer Credentials</div>
      <div class="cred-row">
        <span class="cred-key">Username</span>
        <span class="cred-val">dev@fasafas.com</span>
        <button class="cred-use" onclick="fill('l-user','dev@fasafas.com')">Use</button>
      </div>
      <div class="cred-row">
        <span class="cred-key">Password</span>
        <span class="cred-val">Backend@2026</span>
        <button class="cred-use" onclick="fill('l-pass','Backend@2026')">Use</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="login-footer">
      <a onclick="location.href='../index.html'">← Back to FasaFas</a> ·
      <a onclick="location.href='../admin/'">Admin Portal</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ════════════════════════════════
     DEVELOPER PORTAL
════════════════════════════════ -->
<div id="app-screen">
  <div class="app-layout">

    <!-- ── SIDEBAR ── -->
    <aside class="sidebar">
      <div class="sb-top">
        <div class="sb-logo">
          <div class="sb-logo-dot"></div>
          FasaFas
          <span class="sb-logo-tag">Dev</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sb-user">
        <div class="sb-av">DE</div>
        <div>
          <div class="sb-uname">Dev Engineer</div>
          <div class="sb-urole">Backend Access</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <nav class="sb-nav">
        <div class="sb-section">Architecture</div>
        <div class="sb-item active" onclick="sw('overview',this)"><span class="sb-icon">🗂</span> Overview</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('stack',this)"><span class="sb-icon">🧱</span> Tech Stack</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('services',this)"><span class="sb-icon">⚙️</span> Microservices</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('infra',this)"><span class="sb-icon">☁️</span> Infrastructure</div>

        <div class="sb-section">API Reference</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('rest',this)"><span class="sb-icon">🔌</span> REST Endpoints</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('websocket',this)"><span class="sb-icon">⚡</span> WebSocket / RTC</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('webhooks',this)"><span class="sb-icon">🔗</span> Webhooks</div>

        <div class="sb-section">Data Layer</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('schema',this)"><span class="sb-icon">🗄️</span> Database Schema</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('redis',this)"><span class="sb-icon">⚡</span> Redis & Kafka</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('storage',this)"><span class="sb-icon">📦</span> Storage & CDN</div>

        <div class="sb-section">AI Pipeline</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('ai',this)"><span class="sb-icon">🤖</span> AI Architecture</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('media',this)"><span class="sb-icon">🎬</span> Media Pipeline</div>

        <div class="sb-section">Ops</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('security',this)"><span class="sb-icon">🔒</span> Security Model</div>
        <div class="sb-item" onclick="sw('deploy',this)"><span class="sb-icon">🚀</span> Deployment</div>
      </nav>
      <div class="sb-bottom">
        <button class="logout-btn" onclick="doLogout()">🚪 Sign Out</button>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <!-- ── MAIN ── -->
    <div class="app-main">
      <div class="topbar">
        <div class="topbar-title"><span class="tb-icon" id="tb-icon">🗂</span><span id="tb-title">Architecture Overview</span></div>
        <div class="topbar-right">
          <button class="tb-btn" onclick="showToast('Docs exported to PDF')">⬇ Export Docs</button>
          <button class="tb-btn" onclick="location.href='../index.html'">← Public Site</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content">

        <!-- ── OVERVIEW ── -->
        <div id="panel-overview" class="panel active">
          <div class="ph1">System Architecture Overview</div>
          <div class="pdesc">FasaFas is a microservices-based, cloud-native platform. All services communicate via gRPC internally and expose REST + WebSocket externally. Media flows through a dedicated SFU cluster.</div>
          <div class="g4" style="margin-bottom:22px">
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">Microservices</div><div class="stat-val" style="color:var(--green)">21</div><div class="stat-sub">All independently deployable</div></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">REST Endpoints</div><div class="stat-val" style="color:var(--accent2)">84</div><div class="stat-sub">Versioned under /api/v1</div></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">DB Tables</div><div class="stat-val" style="color:var(--purple)">34</div><div class="stat-sub">PostgreSQL 16 + pgvector</div></div>
            <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-label">WS Events</div><div class="stat-val" style="color:var(--amber)">28</div><div class="stat-sub">Bidirectional Socket.io</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="ph2"><div class="ph2-dot"></div>Request Flow</div>
          <div class="card">
            <ul class="fl">
              <li>Client (Browser / Desktop / Mobile) sends HTTPS request to API Gateway (Nginx + Node.js)</li>
              <li>API Gateway authenticates JWT token via auth-service (Redis token cache, 15 min TTL)</li>
              <li>Gateway routes to appropriate microservice via internal gRPC call</li>
              <li>Service reads/writes PostgreSQL (primary) with read replica fallback</li>
              <li>Real-time events published to Kafka topic → consumed by notification-service → Socket.io push</li>
              <li>Media (audio/video) flows directly to WebRTC SFU cluster — bypasses API gateway entirely</li>
              <li>AI jobs (transcription, summary) enqueued to Kafka → consumed by ai-companion-service</li>
              <li>Files stored to S3-compatible object storage, served via CloudFront CDN with signed URLs</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="ph2"><div class="ph2-dot"></div>Service Communication</div>
          <div class="g2">
            <div class="card"><div class="ph3">Internal (gRPC)</div><ul class="fl">
              <li>All service-to-service calls use gRPC over TLS</li>
              <li>Proto files define strict contracts per service</li>
              <li>Istio service mesh handles retries and circuit breaking</li>
              <li>Deadlines enforced: 5s for sync calls, async via Kafka</li>
            </ul></div>
            <div class="card"><div class="ph3">External (REST + WS)</div><ul class="fl">
              <li>REST API: /api/v1/* — JSON, rate-limited per user</li>
              <li>WebSocket: Socket.io namespaces per feature (/meeting, /chat)</li>
              <li>CORS whitelist: app domain + SDK origins only</li>
              <li>All responses gzip-compressed, ETag caching on GETs</li>
            </ul></div>
          </div>
        </div>

